Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.19,0:01:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.79,0:01:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.73,0:01:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,还是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.37,0:02:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.47,0:02:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,还是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.95,0:02:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ，什麼都不做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.16,0:03:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,昨晚没睡好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.23,0:03:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,新保跟清水老师\N竟然是那种关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.93,0:03:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.27,0:03:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,新保你太令人羡慕了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.23,0:03:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.07,0:03:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我记得
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.64,0:03:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,清水老师不是结婚了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,新保也不可能是她老公
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.94,0:03:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,意思是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.52,0:03:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,和有夫之妇…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.86,0:03:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,什么是有夫之妇？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.70,0:03:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,什么是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.46,0:03:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,夜夜春宵的有夫之妇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.43,0:03:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.50,0:03:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,一大早不要看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.97,0:03:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,有夫之妇指的是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.54,0:03:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,跟男人结了婚的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.87,0:03:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,结婚？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.94,0:03:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.58,0:03:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.45,0:03:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,早上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,现在是做早操的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.89,0:04:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.52,0:04:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,先从手部运动开始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.00,0:04:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.70,0:04:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.00,0:04:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,应该说是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么丝茉茉会在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.71,0:04:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我保管，拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.55,0:04:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这个人果然很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.25,0:04:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…真是的，搞什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.48,0:04:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,到底怎么回事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.39,0:04:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,五分钟后要出门
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,现在不是做这种事的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.93,0:04:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.79,0:04:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,回头见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.93,0:04:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.54,0:05:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉，我迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.75,0:05:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.85,0:05:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,清水老师还没来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.75,0:05:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然有时会早到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.38,0:05:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,可是她从来没迟到过的说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,到底是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.90,0:05:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,清水老师到最后还是没来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.47,0:05:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,新保那家伙也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他们两个到底在搞什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.21,0:05:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.31,0:05:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.61,0:05:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.55,0:05:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉，我要这个跟这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.18,0:05:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.52,0:05:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不过新保那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.39,0:05:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛又要托我保管丝茉茉？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.59,0:05:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.23,0:05:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,学长，手，手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.33,0:05:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.80,0:05:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我到底在搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.21,0:06:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.01,0:06:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么事了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.34,0:06:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.05,0:06:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,要改变时间吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.05,0:06:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,因为棒球比赛转播
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.52,0:06:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,预定录影的节目\N被延后三十分钟了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.59,0:06:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,别这么大声
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.13,0:06:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是我打工的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.96,0:06:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.80,0:06:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,要改变设定时间吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.23,0:06:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,改
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.23,0:06:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,总之回背包里面去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.93,0:06:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,新保
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.84,0:06:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,学长，那台电脑是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.48,0:06:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,新保不知道什么时候\N偷放到我的背包里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.71,0:06:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,说要我帮他保管
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.68,0:06:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,话说回来，干嘛要我保管呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.49,0:06:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,既不会成为包袱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.22,0:06:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,也不会妨碍到他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.99,0:06:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.13,0:07:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不但方便、漂亮\N还什么都会替你做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.83,0:07:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,电脑真的有很多好处
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.87,0:07:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.97,0:07:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我不该对裕美发牢骚的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.47,0:07:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不，没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.47,0:07:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.88,0:07:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不管牢骚还是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.14,0:07:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我都全年无休，照单全收
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.65,0:07:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你，裕美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.35,0:07:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,今天又是一团糟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.32,0:07:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,全都是新保那家伙害的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.02,0:07:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,有电话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.93,0:07:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,请赶快接听
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.63,0:07:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,请赶快接听
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,再响五声
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.36,0:07:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,就会转到答录机模式
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.97,0:07:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我接通
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.54,0:07:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.34,0:07:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.57,0:07:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.47,0:07:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那…那个声音，你是新保对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.24,0:07:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在在搞什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,跟老师私奔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.79,0:07:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.42,0:07:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,要插在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.49,0:08:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得是把这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.39,0:08:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,快出来，快出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.23,0:08:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么没有影像
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.73,0:08:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,快出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.56,0:08:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,快出来，快出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.27,0:08:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.37,0:08:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这边吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.74,0:08:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不，这边才对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.20,0:08:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.74,0:08:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.31,0:08:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这里…那里…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.48,0:08:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,连上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.05,0:08:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨，本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.38,0:08:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,新保
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.18,0:08:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,喔，自己接好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.85,0:08:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,老师我很高兴喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.05,0:08:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.65,0:08:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯什么嗯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.09,0:08:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,私奔是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.96,0:08:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,如同我说的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.29,0:08:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟清水老师现在私奔中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.46,0:08:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我在问你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.43,0:08:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你干嘛跟补习班老师私奔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.87,0:08:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,再说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.87,0:08:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你是什么时候\N跟她开始交往的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.37,0:08:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,已经快半年了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.74,0:08:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是\N刚到补习班上课的时候吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.87,0:08:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然在我不注意时跟老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.61,0:08:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.91,0:09:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,竟敢瞒着我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.58,0:09:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,就算我说了也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.55,0:09:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.72,0:09:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,在这么重要的时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.69,0:09:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.39,0:09:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这台电视不但是旧型  又便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.96,0:09:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我接的方法一定也不对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.93,0:09:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,已经没时间烦恼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.97,0:09:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,现在必须…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.67,0:09:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,秀树
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.14,0:09:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ，我去稔家裡一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.57,0:09:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我马上就回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.14,0:09:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,要乖乖看家喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.88,0:09:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,什么是“私奔”？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.08,0:09:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是好事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.72,0:09:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,还是坏事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.85,0:09:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.52,0:09:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道\N该怎么回答才好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.03,0:09:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,秀树
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.30,0:09:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:09:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.68,0:10:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,补习班学生竟然跟老师私奔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.22,0:10:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他到底在想什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.59,0:10:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,新保这个大混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.33,0:10:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,本须和少爷来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.26,0:10:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,都这么晚了，发生什么事了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.90,0:10:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我去准备本须和少爷的茶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.90,0:10:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,真夸张的出场方式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托将她接到有画面的电话线上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.64,0:10:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你是指超高速通信线路吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.31,0:10:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.21,0:10:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.75,0:10:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,可以是可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.85,0:10:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你想跟谁通电话呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.85,0:10:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,搞私奔的混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.60,0:10:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,已经接上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.03,0:11:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,画面会出现在这里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.34,0:11:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.94,0:11:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,马上会出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧，本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.27,0:11:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.57,0:11:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,喔，你在国分寺家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.44,0:11:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.18,0:11:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,继续刚刚的话题，新保
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.16,0:11:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要瞒着我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.23,0:11:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我先跟你说也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.10,0:11:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,或者应该说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.24,0:11:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直想跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.50,0:11:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,别看我这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.67,0:11:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我可是把你当作朋友喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.61,0:11:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,新保
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.84,0:11:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我也当你是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.85,0:11:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,既然如此，为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.18,0:11:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,因为多香子不同意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.15,0:11:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,多香子是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.35,0:11:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,清水老师的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.12,0:11:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道多香子已经结婚了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.45,0:11:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,老师告诉我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.02,0:11:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,上次在我那边过夜的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.16,0:11:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,她丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.06,0:11:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,结婚之后马上就迷上电脑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.83,0:11:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,夫妻间的谈话\N变得都是电脑的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.17,0:11:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,刚开始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.37,0:11:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,多香子以为他只是\N刚买了电脑高兴过头
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.10,0:11:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,所以也没在意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.01,0:11:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,但一段时间之后\N她丈夫就只跟电脑说话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.28,0:12:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不管多香子在不在他身边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.45,0:12:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,只跟电脑？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.48,0:12:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.65,0:12:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你对电脑不了解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.92,0:12:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,大概想不通吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.89,0:12:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,最近这种人一直在增加
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.05,0:12:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这么说来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.02,0:12:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得电脑比较可爱吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.16,0:12:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,和人类比起来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.89,0:12:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,跟电脑在一起比较快乐吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.36,0:12:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.80,0:12:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那些话就是指这件事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.00,0:12:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,离补习班不远的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.40,0:12:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,有个小公园对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.81,0:12:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,大概是刚到补习班的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.41,0:12:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,某天傍晚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.58,0:12:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我经过那里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.91,0:12:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,多香子她…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.92,0:12:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那时候还是叫她清水老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.79,0:12:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,当时老师她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.59,0:12:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,坐在秋千上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.79,0:12:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,一开始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.13,0:12:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我还以为她只是童心大发
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.73,0:12:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,想玩玩秋千
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.60,0:12:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,所以没有叫她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.97,0:12:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,等我吃完晚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.54,0:13:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,明明已经很晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.74,0:13:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,她却还在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.11,0:13:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.85,0:13:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.08,0:13:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,新保
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.12,0:13:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这里做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.66,0:13:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我回不了家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.33,0:13:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,因为门锁上了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.67,0:13:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你忘了带钥匙了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.57,0:13:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,钥匙我是有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.88,0:13:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,可是上了门链，打不开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.31,0:13:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,门链是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.05,0:13:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,里面有人在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.29,0:13:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.99,0:13:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我老公
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.89,0:13:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,老公？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.14,0:14:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.34,0:14:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你们吵架了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.07,0:14:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,吵架啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.94,0:14:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我们很久没有吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.95,0:14:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,或者应该说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.51,0:14:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,连话都说不上两句
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.55,0:14:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我当时说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.65,0:14:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好好骂他几句不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.45,0:14:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,她摇了摇头
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.72,0:14:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.79,0:14:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,上了门链就表示
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.76,0:14:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我老公忘了我会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.13,0:14:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,应该是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.47,0:14:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,在不在家都没影响了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.38,0:14:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,一想到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.38,0:14:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,就觉得怎样都无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.32,0:15:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,觉得怎样都…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.56,0:15:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,明明在说这么伤心的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.46,0:15:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,她却没有哭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.33,0:15:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.50,0:15:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.07,0:15:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,她其实很想哭出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.57,0:15:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,只是拼命在忍耐罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.21,0:15:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我想至少让她在遇到\N不愉快或伤心的事时
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.51,0:15:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,能够哭个痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.21,0:15:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我迷上她了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.72,0:16:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,从那之后我就穷追不舍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.76,0:16:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,多香子认为
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.92,0:16:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我是补习班学生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.76,0:16:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,她是补习班老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.39,0:16:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,而且已经结婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.10,0:16:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,对我说了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.36,0:16:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,总之我就是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.73,0:16:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,一直追，一直追
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.90,0:16:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.87,0:16:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,就变成了今天这个局面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.01,0:16:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,就算如此，为什么要私奔？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.28,0:16:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,难道只剩这个方法了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.78,0:16:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我们这个年纪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.25,0:16:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,还是小鬼而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.61,0:16:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,以后你打算怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.92,0:16:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,也许就如同你所说的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,那么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.29,0:16:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不过这是我的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.29,0:16:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,决定？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.56,0:16:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,多香子她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.93,0:16:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,变得不相信男性的人类了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.60,0:16:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,她认为就算一开始说喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.20,0:16:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦出现像电脑那样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.77,0:16:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,可以迎合自己的对象
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.41,0:16:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,就会完全改变
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.11,0:16:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好像从没喜欢过一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.24,0:17:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,跟她说过我是不一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.51,0:17:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,可是不管说几次她还是不信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,上次多香子到本须和房间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.49,0:17:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.85,0:17:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,原本打算两人好好谈谈的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.19,0:17:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,谈谈关于我们的将来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.89,0:17:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不过事到临头\N她好像还是害怕了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.80,0:17:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,女人的心还真是难懂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.51,0:17:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.54,0:17:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,所以？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.81,0:17:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,为了不让她跑掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.18,0:17:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,决定私奔到深山的温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.95,0:17:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个好地方喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.05,0:17:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,像这样湿答答的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.55,0:17:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那不过是旅行而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.98,0:17:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,恩恩爱爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.38,0:17:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,对我来说，这算是私奔啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.35,0:17:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,总而言之
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.52,0:17:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,在多香子点头之前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.82,0:17:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我不打算回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.36,0:17:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,点头？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.49,0:17:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.69,0:17:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我再婚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.03,0:17:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,再婚？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.06,0:17:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,再婚，再婚…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.60,0:17:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,再婚是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.07,0:17:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.00,0:17:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,丝茉茉再帮我保管一段时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.50,0:18:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,帮你保管当然没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.41,0:18:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟谁在通电话？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.44,0:18:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,跟本须和啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.32,0:18:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,清水老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.78,0:18:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,比平常性感好几倍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.35,0:18:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,拜罗，本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.82,0:18:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我会再跟你联络的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.82,0:18:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.89,0:18:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,下次…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.13,0:18:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,下次再有什么事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.26,0:18:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,一定要告诉我喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.56,0:18:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.16,0:18:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.23,0:18:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,像我这种重考生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.53,0:18:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,帮不了你太大的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.87,0:18:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不过或许我可以帮上什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.37,0:18:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.34,0:18:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.41,0:18:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,一定要告诉我喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.81,0:18:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.41,0:18:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,一定喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.91,0:18:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.65,0:18:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,新保
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.15,0:18:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的，新保这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.73,0:18:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,真是好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.46,0:18:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,本须和这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.36,0:18:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，是个好人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不过因为人太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.30,0:19:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,结果只能当个商量的对象
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.24,0:19:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,所以，还是在室男
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.17,0:19:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那天晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.34,0:19:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是到本须和房间去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.34,0:19:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.51,0:19:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,害我找了一个晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.88,0:19:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.18,0:19:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.98,0:19:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我闹得很凶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.99,0:19:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,弄得他很疲倦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.46,0:19:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,本须和他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.79,0:19:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来好像很困了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.86,0:19:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,几乎是无意识状态
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.93,0:19:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我试着问了他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.57,0:19:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,已经结婚的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.54,0:19:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不能喜欢上别人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.15,0:19:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.08,0:19:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢上一个人，是无法抗拒的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.42,0:19:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不过这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.22,0:19:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,对自己的另一半
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.32,0:20:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,对喜欢上的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.23,0:20:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,还有对自己都是痛苦的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.56,0:20:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,别在其中徘徊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.96,0:20:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,只要自己觉得自在就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.87,0:20:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,他这么对我说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.61,0:20:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他竟然说得出这种大道理
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.14,0:20:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,明明还是在室男
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.08,0:20:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不过不知为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,心里像是放下一块大石头
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.48,0:20:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,只要自己觉得自在就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.69,0:20:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,听到他这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉轻松多了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.76,0:20:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.89,0:20:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,为了更轻松自在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.66,0:20:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你要到我身边来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.90,0:20:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我还没这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.83,0:20:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,还没，就是表示快了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.67,0:20:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,新保
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.00,0:20:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你真是无忧无虑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.87,0:20:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.04,0:20:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,都到这里来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.34,0:20:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,还叫我新保啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.01,0:20:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那么问题来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.05,0:21:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你猜猜\N我一直想要你怎么叫我？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.49,0:21:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,阿弘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.39,0:21:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,正确答案
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.30,0:21:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你果然是个好人，本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.74,0:21:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.04,0:21:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的，真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.11,0:21:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,虽是好人却没有女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.28,0:21:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,少管我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.15,0:21:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,迷上电脑的丈夫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.29,0:21:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,就算让女孩流泪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.23,0:21:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,还是觉得电脑比较好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.05,0:23:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.58,0:23:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.91,0:23:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,B
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.72,0:23:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,还好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.72,0:23:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,C
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.55,0:23:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,普通
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.45,0:23:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,D
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.09,0:23:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.09,0:23:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,E
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.95,0:23:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,多加努力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.26,0:23:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,F
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.02,0:23:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,要更努力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.62,0:23:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,G
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.36,0:23:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,更更要努力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.29,0:23:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,H
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.06,0:23:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.56,0:23:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.76,0:24:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Chobits 下一回\N「ちぃ，煮飯」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.40,0:24:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,咕噜
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.37,0:24:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我肚子发出的声音
